squish my text, make it a little bit smaller, allowing me to fit a bit more text into my slides.

00:13:59.179 --> 00:14:03.979
Never a great idea to put a lot of text on your slides, but if you're in a pinch and you just want

00:14:03.979 --> 00:14:10.460
things to be a little bit smaller so everything fits, this is a really nice fix. Um, let's also

